cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO 

This paper deals with the task of Vision-and-Language Navigation (VLN), which involves natural language processing, computer vision, and reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper proposes a data augmentation method using counterfactual thinking, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also uses adversarial training, which is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO).
